odoo-companion (2.20.1) noble; urgency=medium

  * Packaged for source builds (Launchpad PPA / openSUSE Build Service).
  * Live attendance in the system tray: check-in time, live worked-time counter,
    last check-out with date.
  * Smart "you haven't checked in" warning that respects the working-hours
    calendar, public holidays, time off and a configurable grace window.
  * Hardened autostart: background service starts on login after every reboot
    and never stops retrying (StartLimitIntervalSec=0).
  * All module pages with donut/bar charts, filters, search-as-you-type and
    sortable, clickable tables that open the Odoo record.

 -- Rafiur Rahman Rafit <support@dotbdsolutions.com>  Wed, 24 Jun 2026 00:40:26 +0600
